# Underreported News Site

Mobile‑friendly Next.js + Tailwind site that surfaces overlooked stories. Includes mock API and ready‑to‑deploy config.

## Features
- Responsive, mobile‑first UI (Tailwind)
- Dark mode via `prefers-color-scheme`
- API route with mock stories (`/api/stories`)
- Ready for Vercel deploy (`vercel.json`)

## Quick start

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
